Use some of the how-to language for this app:

https://remember.defn.io/
https://github.com/Bogdanp/remember

$ npm init
$ npm install electron electron-rebuild electron-panel-window -save

Rebuild the electron-panel-window module for our versions

$ ./node_modules/.bin/electron-rebuild

Create main.js, index.html and preload.js as required.

Add this to "scripts" section of package.json:

```json
    "start": "electron .",
```

Then run:

$ npm start
